  "reference_number": "RUS3394",
  "remarks": "\nThe Secretary of State considers that there are reasonable grounds to suspect that \nIMO 9037123 (“AS CALCUTTA”) is involved in activity whose object or effect is to destabilise Ukraine or undermine or threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine or to obtain a benefit from or support the Government of Russia. Namely, IMO 9037123 is involved in carrying oil or oil products that originated in Russia from Russia to a third country. \n",
